          				<h3>Acklnowledgements</h3>
          				<p>I would like to acknowledge Charlie Strachan for his time and patience, Jane Oliver Lange, Helen Cunningham, and Tin Pang for allowing me to vent my frustrations and the entire cast and crew of "Leader Of The Pack," who have all assisted me in my many pursuits.</p>
